WEBVTT

00:00:28.934 --> 00:00:31.170
i to se zove slobodnim padom.

00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:32.468
Zapravo padate ka Zemlji.

00:00:32.468 --> 00:00:34.260
U redu, razmislite o ovome na sekund.

00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:35.488
To je osećaj koji imate

00:00:35.488 --> 00:00:37.450
ako krećete preko vrha tobogana,

00:00:37.450 --> 00:00:40.286
idete kao: "Vaaaau!"

00:00:40.286 --> 00:00:41.602
Samo što ovo radite stalno

00:00:41.602 --> 00:00:42.771
dok kružite Zemljom

00:00:42.771 --> 00:00:43.490
dva,

00:00:43.490 --> 00:00:44.021
tri,

00:00:44.021 --> 00:00:44.619
četiri

00:00:44.619 --> 00:00:45.147
sata,

00:00:45.147 --> 00:00:45.720
dana,

00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:46.658
koliko god, zar ne?

00:00:46.658 --> 00:00:48.711
Kako onda funkcioniše
kruženje oko planete?

00:00:48.711 --> 00:00:50.320
Posavetujmo se sa Isakom Njutnom.

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:51.369
Imao je ovu zamisao,

00:00:51.369 --> 00:00:52.621
mali misaoni eksperiment.

00:00:52.621 --> 00:00:53.835
Uzmete top,

00:00:53.835 --> 00:00:54.994
stavite ga na vrh brda.

00:00:54.994 --> 00:00:56.283
Ako ispalite đule,

00:00:56.283 --> 00:00:57.980
ono se malo udalji.

00:00:57.980 --> 00:00:59.534
Ali ukoliko ga ispalite jače,

00:00:59.534 --> 00:01:01.620
ode dovoljno daleko da se spusti